{
  "id": "60437ffda8e2ca001c8e6380",
  "title": "パクチー",
  "created": 1615036431,
  "updated": 1776735089,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "60437ffda8e2ca001c8e6380",
      "text": "パクチー",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1615036431,
      "updated": 1615036431
    },
    {
      "id": "6043800f8ee92a00005fcb1f",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/7e778d3d72aa9af4e3aec2769486ee00]",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1615036431,
      "updated": 1615036431
    },
    {
      "id": "6043800f8ee92a00005fcb20",
      "text": " タイ語",
      "userId": "60e9e764c588100023fa8faf",
      "created": 1615036431,
      "updated": 1626425420
    },
    {
      "id": "6043800f8ee92a00005fcb21",
      "text": " [コリアンダー]ともいう",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1615036431,
      "updated": 1615036431
    },
    {
      "id": "60f2167c5b98c20000aa35fb",
      "text": " 香菜（シャンツァイ）ともいう",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1626478205,
      "updated": 1626478261
    },
    {
      "id": "6043800f8ee92a00005fcb22",
      "text": " 嫌いな人も多いようだ",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1615036431,
      "updated": 1615036431
    },
    {
      "id": "6043800f8ee92a00005fcb23",
      "text": " [増井俊之.icon] は好き",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1615036431,
      "updated": 1615036445
    },
    {
      "id": "613312acad2a1800006a999d",
      "text": " カメムシの匂いがして嫌い[sekiyasu.icon]",
      "userId": "606814ae11bf57001cad2a18",
      "created": 1630737068,
      "updated": 1630737085
    },
    {
      "id": "604380188ee92a00005fcb24",
      "text": " 最初嫌いで、今は好物になりました[kidooom.icon]",
      "userId": "5df97d83ccfabb0017a19e40",
      "created": 1615036441,
      "updated": 1630743512
    },
    {
      "id": "61332bcaa19e400000d5c915",
      "text": "　[タイ]に行った時、タイ人のガイドが「タイ人も半分は嫌いよ」と言っていた",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1630743499,
      "updated": 1630751155
    },
    {
      "id": "61332be9a19e400000d5c917",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5df97d83ccfabb0017a19e40",
      "created": 1630743529,
      "updated": 1630743532
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6d2e80000000000cf2c10",
      "text": "名前が他人の空似すぎる[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776734952,
      "updated": 1776735089
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6d2f10000000000cf2c12",
      "text": " パクチーは名前が凄く韓国っぽい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776734960,
      "updated": 1776734974
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6d3250000000000cf2c17",
      "text": " \tパクとかコリアとか",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776735013,
      "updated": 1776735031
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6d2fe0000000000cf2c14",
      "text": " 実際は、",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776734974,
      "updated": 1776734995
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6d3130000000000cf2c16",
      "text": " \tパクチーはタイ語由来で、",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776734995,
      "updated": 1776734996
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6d3100000000000cf2c15",
      "text": " \tコリアンダーはラテン語のコリアンドルム（coriandrum）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776734992,
      "updated": 1776735001
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6d33e0000000000cf2c18",
      "text": " \t朝鮮の英語 Korea の方は高麗由来で別ルート",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776735037,
      "updated": 1776735067
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6d2e80000000000cf2c11",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776734952,
      "updated": 1776734952
    },
    {
      "id": "6043801f8ee92a00005fcb25",
      "text": "#食材 #野菜",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1615036447,
      "updated": 1615036453
    },
